Package: roc
Type: Package
Title: R tools for ocean colour.
Version: 0.0.7
Date: 2015-04-30
Author: Michael D. Sumner
Maintainer: Michael D. Sumner<mdsumner@gmail.com>
Description: Read HDF4 format Ocean Colour Level-3 bin files. Future releases
    will read from the new NASA NetCDF4 format.
License: GPL-3
LazyLoad: yes
Depends: dplyr
Imports:
    geosphere,
    Rcpp (>= 0.11.2),
    sp,
    raadtools,
    raster,
    rgdal
Suggests:
    rrshdf, 
    testthat
LinkingTo: Rcpp
NeedsCompilation: yes
